{"tid":1220788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為稱Verizon應支付10億美元專利許可費","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:02:56.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8368325fb0a7d2f1ec76b2fd10d7d338497f7e2a","tid":1220788,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"華為稱Verizon應支付10億美元專利許可費<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462561-20190613.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462561-20190613.htm&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWCJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=1b83d0ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462561-20190613.htm&h=34cf7eff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462561-20190613.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n外電引述消息人士報道，中國華為認為美國電訊商Verizon應該支付230多項華為專利許可費，總計超過10億美元。<br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報較早時報道，華為一名負責知識產權許可的高級管理人員2月時曾去信Verizon，認為對方應支付費用以解決專利許可問題。消息人士說，有關專利涉及Verizon 20多家供應商的網路設備，包括美國主要科技公司，但有關供應商可以向Verizon追回費用。華為已直接聯繫部分科技公司。<br />\n<br />\n報道提到，有關專利涉及核心網路設備、有線基礎設施同物聯網技術。Verizon及有關公司已通知美國政府。<br />\n<br />\nVerizon發言人未有具體評論，因為是潛在法律問題，但指出事件不單止涉及Verizon。"},{"pid":"e5a1998a04a51600ddbc36f2a524149f4b18cb46","tid":1220788,"uid":38535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:02:56.000Z","msg":"即係好似&quot;新百伦&quot;告new balance 咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}